10 spectacular dark wallpapers for iPhone
03 Nov 2019, 20:00 by Artyom Bausov
It's time to change the images on your desktop. This time we suggest putting dark pictures.
Have collected 10 spectacular wallpapers for your iPhone.
How to install this wallpaper on iPhone
It is very simple and is done in two stages - downloading and installing a background image.
1. Open the picture on a separate screen by tapping the link below the image. After that, click on it and hold for 2-3 seconds -> Save Image (or Add to Photo in iOS 13).
2. To set the image as a background, go to Settings -> Wallpaper -> Select new wallpaper and select the downloaded picture.
3. Click the Install button.
